snippet.title: Puyo Puyo (1992, Arcade) - 2 of 2: EN Version (Hardest)[1080p60]
snippet.description:
Pyon-Pyon!

Hardest difficulty throughout the longplay.

Also, the moment when you had to out-spin Harpy (of all the opponents in this game!)
